data.description: *Back on the Market no fault of the sellers*Take a look at this move in ready home on a corner lot. Upon entering you’ll be greeted by a gracious front porch (where you could have your morning coffee). As you walk through the front door, you will be delightfully surprised by the gleaming hardwood floors and traditional floor plan that includes a living room, dining room, quaint kitchen (that includes range and refrigerator) two bedrooms, and one bath. This home also has an open basement that could be finished for extra space. This home has all new pex-piping, a New Tear off roof and Newer HVAC. All repairs have been completed. Make an appointment to see it today.
